---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Services">
  <h1>Services</h1>
  <ul class="card-list">
    <li>
      <service-card href="/services/design" title="Design">
        <p slot="content">
          I offer UI/UX design services focused on creating intuitive and
          user-friendly interfaces that enhance the overall user experience. My
          approach involves understanding user needs and translating them into
          visually appealing and functional designs. I have experience in
          developing component-based architectures and reusable UI elements,
          which promotes consistency and maintainability across projects. Key
          areas of my design service include wireframing, prototyping, user flow
          mapping, and ensuring designs are accessible and performant. I aim to
          deliver designs that not only meet aesthetic goals but also drive user
          engagement and satisfaction.
        </p>
      </service-card>
    </li>
    <li>
      <service-card href="/services/hosting" title="Hosting">
        <p slot="content">
          I provide reliable and scalable hosting solutions tailored to your
          needs. Whether it's a personal blog or a complex web application, I
          can help you deploy and manage your project on various platforms. My
          services include server setup, maintenance, performance optimization,
          and ensuring high availability and security for your website or
          application.
        </p>
      </service-card>
    </li>
    <li>
      <service-card title="Consultation">
        <p slot="content">
          I offer expert consultation services to help you navigate the
          complexities of software development. Whether you need guidance on
          technology choices, project planning, or overcoming specific technical
          challenges, I can provide strategic advice and practical solutions. My
          consultation services are designed to empower you with the knowledge
          and insights needed to make informed decisions and achieve your
          project goals effectively.
        </p>
      </service-card>
    </li>
  </ul>
  <contact-component href="https://calendar.app.google/t9p2HfknyNWf1RNV6"
  ></contact-component>
</Layout>
<style>
  a {
    all: unset;
    cursor: pointer;
  }

  ul {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 2rem;
    list-style-type: none;
  }
</style>
<script>
  import "../components/card/service-card";
  import "../components/contact";
</script>
